    "Also, millennials are seen as a digitally savvy age group with heightened trend awareness (Aslam et al., 2022).",
    "Including millennials is prompted by the AI industry's need to pay attention to younger generations, who are more likely to be early adopters of emerging technologies (Szymkowiak et al., 2021).",
